<div class="section">

  <div class="service-block">
    <div class="icon">🏠</div>
    <div>
      <h3>Home Insurance</h3>
      <p>Your home is your most valuable asset. Our home insurance policies protect your property, your belongings, and your personal liability — all in one package tailored to you.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Homeowner and tenant policies</li>
        <li>Coverage for fire, theft, water damage, and more</li>
        <li>Personal liability protection</li>
        <li>Optional add-ons for jewelry, home office, and more</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="service-block">
    <div class="icon">🚗</div>
    <div>
      <h3>Auto Insurance</h3>
      <p>Whether you drive a sedan, an SUV, or a motorcycle, we'll find you competitive auto coverage through our network of top-rated insurers. We compare so you don't have to.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Standard and high-risk auto coverage</li>
        <li>Multi-vehicle discounts</li>
        <li>Comprehensive and collision coverage</li>
        <li>Motorcycle and recreational vehicle insurance</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="service-block">
    <div class="icon">🏢</div>
    <div>
      <h3>Commercial Insurance</h3>
      <p>Running a business comes with real risks. We build commercial packages that cover your property, your liability, your employees, and everything in between — so you can focus on your work.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Commercial general liability (CGL)</li>
        <li>Property and equipment coverage</li>
        <li>Contractors and trades packages</li>
        <li>Errors & Omissions (E&O) for professionals</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="service-block">
    <div class="icon">👷</div>
    <div>
      <h3>Union Insurance</h3>
      <p>BSMW has long-standing experience working with unions and their members. We offer group rates and individual plans designed specifically for union employees and their families.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Group home and auto rates for union members</li>
        <li>Life and disability coverage</li>
        <li>Flexible plans that work around union benefit packages</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

